Title: Dark Star
Plot: As half-term approaches, Rose is on a training course and Oscar and Carrie are expectantly awaiting an exciting new mission at HQ. Frank, however, receives a call and suddenly sends them home. Across town, Colt Winchester is broken out of prison by his two cohorts. They are going straight after Fran
